name: splainer
description: Splainer is the Search Sandbox that helps you understand why!
full_description:
The sandbox that explains your search results for you so you don't have to go digging through explain debug! Paste in your Solr or Elasticsearch URL and go.

Learn more at https://github.com/o19s/splainer.

Run it via `docker run -d -p 9000:9000 o19s/splainer` and browse to http://localhost:9000
